{"tid":1342310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣組】做嘢！！ 我地做返文宣野！！！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:26:24.000Z","uid":73540,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"35f5d0df463de1ca94b9bc9b7e41e3027b329120","tid":1342310,"uid":73540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"有人認為港共係玩以下手段：<br />\n<br />\n準備聽日開始面對成套建制文宣<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「拿 反對警察呀嘛 咪唔撚幫你囉 自食其果啦<br />\n日日示威攪到人 人地咪打你囉 其他市民都有忍耐限度嫁」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地要做野！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgZKFwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgZKFwt.jpg&h=8ab031d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家<br />\n1. 港共將上環示威者同元朗班鄕黑混為一談<br />\n2. 應對以下奶共權貴鄕黑荒謬講法<br />\n「拿 反對警察呀嘛 咪唔撚幫你囉 自食其果啦<br />\n日日示威攪到人 人地咪打你囉 其他市民都有忍耐限度嫁」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最重要係拉攏住啲游離份子！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do0dRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do0dRB.jpg&h=ff8e7ff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日好多中年老年人一齊行<br />\n佢地知道我地係和平嘅<br />\n亦有好多人因為旺角、沙田衝突，而同情學生<br />\n<br />\n今次班鄕黑搞事，係加大咗個白色恐怖<br />\n要人收聲<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 要分返示威者「5大訴求」，講明前因後果，點解會升級<br />\n2. 要減低市民恐懼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrCPRDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrCPRDL.jpg&h=5350b31f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5e59246f3c8d410fbbbdc4088c43e7696835e60","tid":1342310,"uid":216907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>【 緊急】集中火力攻「警黑一家，警黑合作」輿論戰！唔可以俾政府同黑社會割席！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1341889\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1341889</a>"},{"pid":"1c691b01cc09ee49f22e672cb8667ceb15f875d8","tid":1342310,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"何君堯與黑社會片已upload youtube&amp;streamable SHARE<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1341994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1341994</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n快去加英文字幕比左外國記者先"},{"pid":"c8ea51ec59edf4f9780a0303152802174211612a","tid":1342310,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:28:01.000Z","msg":"28/7 元朗反黑遊行（廣傳）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yl287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyl287&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1KC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0c6443c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yl287</a>"},{"pid":"dcee1d0b9b2a2b337ac56fab080774603ca5a3a5","tid":1342310,"uid":36726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"[Reddit]將警黑合作推出國際<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1340767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1340767</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一齊推到上reddit熱門！"},{"pid":"3d63c14a5d40412ce77c49a01d692fb47426f987","tid":1342310,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1338170/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返唔到屋企嘅手足入黎!! 有地方落腳!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d4b4bb0e7063356f948c18448ecf8cb24b3679","tid":1342310,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求：</span></strong><br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士、撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會、並追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>追究元朗暴徒行兇、警察失蹤</str